{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"http://ghost.local:8000","title":"vwa.la help","description":"Everything you need to know about the vwa.la influencer marketing platform."}},"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Installation Guide","date":null,"date_pretty":null,"path":null,"meta_title":"How to install, uninstall and re-install","meta_description":"","image":null,"next":null,"sidebar":"merchant","toc":null,"keywords":["merchant","help"]},"html":"<h2 id=\"installation\"><a href=\"#installation\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Installation</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://Vwa.la\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Vwa.la</a> can be quickly installed in two ways:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>From the Shopify app store <a href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/vwala\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://apps.shopify.com/vwala</a> or;</li>\n<li>From the our <a href=\"https://www.vwa.la/#/s/create\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">merchant signup page.</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>During installation, we ask that you specify your base promotion and select a billing plan.</p>\n<h4 id=\"base-promotion\"><a href=\"#base-promotion\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Base Promotion</h4>\n<p>In this step, you'll create a base promotion that will apply to all of your influencers and products. Promotions are a powerful selling tool that you can use to maximise the effectiveness of your influencer marketing program. To learn more, read our <a href=\"/merchant/promotions\">promotions guide</a>.</p>\n<h4 id=\"billing-plan\"><a href=\"#billing-plan\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Billing Plan</h4>\n<p>The final step is to choose a billing plan. We offer a 14 day free trial. Don't worry so much about choosing the right sized plan, you can upgrade/downgrade or even cancel your plan at any point. To read more about our pricing, please see our <a href=\"https://www.vwa.la/#/pricing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">pricing tables</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"uninstalls\"><a href=\"#uninstalls\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Uninstalls</h2>\n<h1 id=\"taking-a-break\"><a href=\"#taking-a-break\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Taking a break</h1>\n<p>To pause your vwa.la account, you can contact us, or you can simply update your promotion policy so that your influencers receive $0 or 0% commission on orders.</p>\n<h1 id=\"full-uninstall\"><a href=\"#full-uninstall\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Full uninstall</h1>\n<p>You can uninstall <a href=\"http://vwa.la\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">vwa.la</a> at anytime using your Shopify admin console (apps section). This will disable your influencer marketing program. We'll let your influencers know too, that way they are aware that their links / codes will no longer be usable. </p>\n<h2 id=\"re-installs\"><a href=\"#re-installs\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Re-installs</h2>\n<p>Should you wish to re-install <a href=\"http://vwa.la\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">vwa.la</a> at a later time, you can follow the same steps outlined in the installation section above. Re-installing <a href=\"http://vwa.la\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">vwa.la</a> will restore your accounts data and re-activate your influencer marketing program's promotions, links and discount codes.</p>\n<p>Need more info? We're here to help, simply click the chat icon on the bottom-right to start a conversation.</p>","fields":{"slug":"/merchant/installation-guide/"},"timeToRead":2,"excerpt":"Installation Vwa.la  can be quickly installed in two ways: From the Shopify app store  https://apps.shopify.com/vwala  or; From the ourâ€¦"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/merchant/installation-guide/"}}